==Description== <!--T:2-->

<!--T:3-->
The [[Image:Sketcher_CreateSlot.svg|24px]] [[Sketcher_CreateSlot|Sketcher CreateSlot]] tool creates a slot, a closed polyline consisting of two semicircles connected by two parallel straight lines.

